House Bill 478
By: Representative Kendrick of the 95th
A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Part 2 of Article 15 of Chapter 1 of Title 10 of the Official Code of Georgia
2 Annotated, relating to the Fair Business Practices Act, so as to require that AI generated
3 content used in commerce and trade include a disclaimer indicating such content was
4 generated using artificial intelligence; to provide for the form of such disclaimers; to provide
5 for a definition; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other
6 purposes.
7 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
8 SECTION 1.
9 Part 2 of Article 15 of Chapter 1 of Title 10 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated,
10 relating to the Fair Business Practices Act, is amended in Code Section 10-1-392, relating
11 to definitions, by adding a new paragraph to read as follows:
12 "(.1) 'AI generated content' means a video recording, video file, audio recording, audio
13 file, still image, or still image file that is created through the use of an engineered or
14 machine based system that emulates the capability of a person to receive audio, visual,
15 text, or any other form of information and use the information received to emulate a
16 human cognitive process, including, but not limited to, learning, generalizing, reasoning,
